    "It may be composed of multiple internal components and thus may be deployed over different VMs.",
    "The VNFs are usually connected together to support a required service.• The MANO is responsible for the management of the NFVI and the life cycle of the instantiated VNFs.",
    "It includes the required functionalities for the configuration and orchestration of VNFs respecting the deployment model and the properties of the supported service.",
    "While both industry and academia adopt NFV at remarkable speed, its development is still at early stage and many questions remain open.",
    "Different techniques are used to solve these problems and one particularly interesting and promising one is machine learning, introduced below."
